description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 74, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 222, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 1 for East, Nine Lives for South, and Box for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60743-91940-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [222 Votes, Top 5% Score]
